4:
Heh. There's no use resisting. You're
just wasting your breath.
8:
P-please... Whatever you do, at least
spare our lives!
11:
Gahahah! We'll see if I'm feeling
generous—but no promises!
18:
TEN—the heavens shake—
CHI—the earth bellows—
JIN—man cries out.
Together, they beckon me to
cleanse the world of evil!
21:
Hear me, villains! You cannot
escape the destiny that awaits you
at the edge of my hyper-oscillating
blade!
25:
My name is Zantetsu—warrior of
justice! Prepare to receive your
judgment!
28:
Who the hell is this weirdo?
What're you waiting for? Take him
out already!
38:
Are you unhurt? Flee this place while
you have the chance!
41:
Y-yes... We shall.
Thank you for your help, great
clockwork samurai!
43: We are forever in your debt!
46: Oh, is it already over? That was fast...
50:
But of course! Opportunities are to
be seized, not brooded over. The
next soul in need awaits us, after all!
60:
I know not!
But if we search, we are bound to
find them!
65:
Isn't that just poking our noses
where they don't belong?
70:
Tsk, tsk, tsk! Of course not, Lord
Nimbus.
74:
To expend all one's effort for the
sake of the weak—without a
moment's hesitation—is the very
ESSENCE of a hero.
78:
Come! Let us away—swiftly, as the
wind.
89:
All that looking and we found
nothing...
97:
What ever do you mean? It is most
fortuitous that we were able to meet
again, honorable samurai. Please,
stay for dinner—
106:
So, you lowlives went and hired
bodyguards, did you?
108:
Consider this your punishment for
going against us!
Men, attack!
114:
Showing not a grain of remorse, you
deign to harm innocents again? My
blade shall teach you the discipline
you sorely lack!
117:
Gah, that freak samurai again! This
is a job for you, Gonzaburo!
124:
Hahaha! You thought a simple
blade was going to work on
Gonzaburo? Think again!
129:
To endanger the lives of innocents
so... Gonzaburo!
You are truly a fiend most vile!
144:
What the hell are you standing
around for?! Finish the damn blob
off already!
155:
Seriously, Stella, you've gotta cut it
out with these reckless stunts...
158: I'm okay. Zantetsu was here with me.
163:
At least she didn't get injured or
anything!
168:
M-most astonishing... Lady Stella...
Perhaps you too have the
wherewithal to be a ninja samurai!
171:
I must encourage you to hone this
latent skill! If you wish, I could even
school you in the fundamentals.
175:
Then you will be an ally of justice in
both mind and body! What say you?!
178: I would like to hear more about it.
182:
A samurai ninja lecture done by Sir
Dorksalot? That's gonna be a hard
pass for me.
186:
To be honest, it does sound pretty
cool. It's probably worth a listen.
191:
Excellent. The way of the ninja
samurai is one of eternal adoration
of peace. Our supreme duty is to
help those in need.
192:
To protect the weak, we must be
willing to endure even great pains to
our bodies. That is the spirit of
Yamato!
196:
No matter the hour, no matter the
peril, it is our duty to strive and fight
until the bitter end—to ensure that
not a soul is left behind!
201: Okay. I will strive and fight.
206:
But a ninja samurai is not merely
powerful! They must be
ever-vigilant—and all the while
remain unshakable and composed.
207:
After committing to their most
honorable mission, they must never
falter, never lose their way. They will
always choose the righteous path!
211: Okay. I won't lose my way.
215:
Lady Stella, if you can take these
teachings to heart, then you too can
become a ninja samurai.
225:
But perhaps... it was foolish of me to
assume I needed to impart this
upon you.
229:
The soul of a hero already burns
strong within you! I preach to a
believer!
231:
I implore you—use the spirit of the
ninja samurai that rests inside you
for the betterment of others!
238:
Excellent, excellent.
Well then, I must be off to patrol! If
you'll excuse me.
252:
Another successful mission.
Operating like this in secret truly is
the way of the—
256:
Of the... ninja samurai.
And yet I wonder...
258:
Do I perhaps only do this...
for the satisfaction it provides me?
